*Uhvatio* je njegov pas zeca za rep (He caught his dog chasing a rabbit.)

*Uhvati* ga, on je kriv za sve što se desilo (Catch him, he is responsible for all that happened.)

*Uhvaćen* je u krivu situaciju (He was caught in a wrong situation.)

*Uhvatiće* ga bezbednosne službe (The security services will capture him.)